      <title>特朗普就堕胎问题攻击哈里斯，这是他很少讨论的话题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/trump-attacks-harris-on-abortion-an-issue-he-rarely-discusses</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 在堕胎问题上攻击民主党，试图将自己定位为这一问题的温和派，同时将重点转向新的大选挑战者副总统卡马拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris)。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/trump-attacks-harris-on-abortion-an-issue-he-rarely-discusses</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 00:45:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚加入美国制裁约旦河西岸的以色列定居者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/australia-joins-us-in-sanctioning-israeli-settlers-in-west-bank</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚因定居者在约旦河西岸对巴勒斯坦人实施暴力而对七名以色列人实施了经济制裁和旅行禁令，此举加入美国、日本和其他国家对该地区极端分子的打击行列。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/australia-joins-us-in-sanctioning-israeli-settlers-in-west-bank</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 23:31:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞秋·里夫斯首次出国访问称英国“开放营商”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/rachel-reeves-says-uk-open-for-business-in-first-overseas-trip</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯将在上任后的首次海外访问中向国际同行表示英国“对商业持开放态度”，她将延续新工党政府推动经济增长的举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/rachel-reeves-says-uk-open-for-business-in-first-overseas-trip</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>IFS 称英国央行加息导致 32 万人陷入贫困</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/boe-rate-rises-pushed-320-000-more-people-into-poverty-ifs-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政研究所估计，由于英国央行决定将借贷成本提高至 16 年来的最高水平，英国将有 32 万新增贫困人口。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/boe-rate-rises-pushed-320-000-more-people-into-poverty-ifs-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登在椭圆形办公室演讲中表示，是时候听取“年轻人的声音”了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/biden-to-cast-exit-as-bid-to-unite-nation-in-oval-office-address</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登在结束连任竞选和政治生涯后的首次讲话中表示，他退出 2024 年大选的重大决定是为了在新一代领导人的领导下团结国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/biden-to-cast-exit-as-bid-to-unite-nation-in-oval-office-address</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 22:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
